WEBVTT

00:00:01.480 --> 00:00:03.376
Strap yourselves in,

00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:05.376
we're going to Mars.

00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:07.496
Not just a few astronauts --

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:10.656
thousands of people
are going to colonize Mars.

00:00:10.680 --> 00:00:13.800
And I am telling you
that they're going to do this soon.

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:17.536
Some of you will end up
working on projects on Mars,

00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:20.920
and I guarantee that some
of your children will end up living there.

00:00:21.760 --> 00:00:24.136
That probably sounds preposterous,

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:27.040
so I'm going to share with you
how and when that will happen.

